work.summary:
Co-founded a startup focused in Computer Vision products. Worked as a lead developer (back-end/front-end and ML) creating different systems that went to production:
- Face Recognition/Liveness models and API scalable to millions of images;
- OCR for text documents (text detection/recognition, NLP, Key Information Extraction);
- Object detection (logo, license plate recognition)
These technologies help the company to be acquired by an unicorn Brazilian startup Unico ID Tech. Some of this past work can still be found in this medium page: https://medium.com/@meerkat.cv
